02:40.841 --> 02:43.639
I'm alone, and I want
to keep it that way.

02:43.710 --> 02:46.304
I lost my wife and son.

02:46.379 --> 02:50.145
- Well, ask the bartender.
He can find anything.
- No.

02:50.217 --> 02:52.014
They're dead.

02:54.855 --> 02:57.415
Do you wanna talk about it?

