Yeah?
Why is that?

01:39:20.565 --> 01:39:22.999
- Because on an intimacy scale...
- Mm-hmm.

01:39:23.067 --> 01:39:25.160
having somebody watch me
brush my teeth...

01:39:25.236 --> 01:39:27.830
is right up there with seeing me
on a Sazerac swing...

01:39:27.905 --> 01:39:29.998
- and I'm not minding it.
- [Laughing]

